#. Description of the plugin
#: agnosis.php
msgid ""
"Art blooming out of oblivion. Email your art, AI polishes it, the world sees "
"it. A free, federated publishing network for independent artists."
msgstr ""
"Aṣa ti n yọ jade lati inu airotẹlẹ. Firanṣẹ iṣẹ ọnà rẹ nipasẹ imeeli, AI n "
"ṣe itọju rẹ, aye naa n ri i. Nẹtiwọọki ikede ọfẹ, ti o ni ifowosowopo fun "
"awọn oṣere ominira."

